Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.83,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.51,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:49.14,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:53.32,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:57.14,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:01.04,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:03.94,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:08.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.87,0:23:12.60,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:19.10,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:21.04,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:22.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:26.93,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:31.55,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:34.72,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.86,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.48,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:42.85,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.66,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:47.05,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:50.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:55.17,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
