Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鞋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我来送府上掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叽叽 我回来啦狒狒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 好累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿被捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～命运的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 没鞋子回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 带我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不算近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是从这里跳出去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让她不要跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她不听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很少有机会来女孩子的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张心跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君不会去女朋友家玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有…女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嗬～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 留下来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨也要上夜班 不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们请我果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野 不能让姐姐太担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 客人是头一次来我们店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要剪头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎样剪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恋爱 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱要怎样才会顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是「主动出击了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然剧本还没写好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次有吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戏～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}（和子妄想中）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这次是男女的吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这一定会成为话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想制造话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧就是宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看官的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台才真正成为舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那角色分配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我印象中女方应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长 和子大人是皆水大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…到底不能让岛上神圣的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人前深吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对方是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我郑重申请候补
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻气盛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻…主动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.08,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs20\fsp1}（YoungGanGan 刊载本作漫画的杂志）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言传出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说下一部剧有吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下得了手啊 沙里奈部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手要是拓人君 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想申请候补呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是谁 果然是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君不会是初吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是吻 也只是演戏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体Ayingott的复生启动准备即将就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayingott之眼不能用第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在使用素体本体功能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二阶段以上才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了寻找巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要驾驶员人面狮乘坐电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能找出下落不明的巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要解开日死之巫女的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的素体就能进入第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Tauburn的战斗也会变得更有利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我几时可以驯化Ayingott？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成功 就看你的欲望了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就等这一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始复出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二场庆典开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们放逐时代的时代终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表困扰我一晚的吻戏角色分配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次的吻戏是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君和水野酱的新手组合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}（拓人巴士）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园里已经引起相当大的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现鞠野～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情似乎很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我首次登台就要演吻戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜对方是谁～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮咚 叮咚 叮咚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 感情不错的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戏的女角 原来不是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了么 令人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作画时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真的很乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑造世界的重负与欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘画或许就是体验神的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这确实是段非常幸福的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画喜欢的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想画一幅你的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃冰淇淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是什么味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鞠野一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜我选了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊 次次中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着和自己这么相像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拓人接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果这是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就必须捍卫它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我正是为此而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成Ayingott的奥利哈康
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始光子活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人还真少见啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都得一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院祭上要亲嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您咋知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷唷 唷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayingott…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是Ayingott
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人特别讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你的回归
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人切身体会到第三阶段近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayingott之眼启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够找出巫女藏身之所的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么只有那台素体被捏碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许应更为慎重考虑为好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方的…巫女们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…由我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…贪食我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面狮打算一举击败银河美少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是人面狮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Ayingott自己在发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁的心 被禁锢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是台邪恶的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该让它复活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来救你 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪快 银河十字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 和子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有接吻经历？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷 唷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间过程中 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助Ayingott的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日死之巫女现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面狮似乎察觉了你的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公之于众其实也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像决定 不说多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 Ayingott的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机能正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有柱之印记的人降生那年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上必会有四位巫女同时降生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以认为谎言可以蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 拓人果然很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么让她开口好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要包庇的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩即是 日死之巫女
Comment: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鸦之介是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近最喜欢拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊吧 驯化！
